title: AHS Cult - Ivy death scene
author: Ahs Queens
comment: I love how this was one of the rare TV shows that did not show a LGBT couple as perfect and adorable.
I love how she's wearing a sweater with small holes, conquering her fear.
Moral Lesson: You don't eat and drink while that person is talking about revenge.

Ivy:
-Set up her wife to shoot an innocent man
-Is a murderer 
-Joined a cult to make her wife go insane

"You'll never do anything to me."

"I already have." Sarah Paulson always delivers. 🙌
